title: AHS: DOUBLE FEATURE | Official Teaser Trailer (HQ)
author: AHS Crave
comment: Looks like we will be getting aliens.
I’m so excited to see this
description: American Horror Story Season 10 "Double Feature" premieres August 25 on FX! The first half of the season, "Red Tide," stars Sarah Paulson as TB Karen, Evan Peters as Austin, Lily Rabe as Doris Gardner, Finn Wittrock as Harry Gardner, Frances Conroy as Belle Noir, Billie Lourd as Lark, Leslie Grossman as Ursula, Adina Porter as Chief Burelson, Angelica Ross as The Chemist, and Macaulay Culkin as Mickey! The second half of the season, "Death Valley," stars Kaia Gerber, Nico Greetham, Isaac Cole Powell, John Carroll Lynch, Rachel Hilson, and Neal McDonough!
